@WG-prioritization/alerts issue #85264 has been requested for prioritization.

Procedure

  • Priority?
  • Regression?
  • Notify people/groups?
  • Needs I-nominated?

Another one from the fallout of #83278, this wasnt caught because the crater run (iiuc) runs cargo check and Mark makes the point of running a deeper crate run (which hopefully should reveal more breakages).
regardless of why, I understand here that there are breaking changes but I dont understand from the comments if they could have been documented
so by my limited context I'd either assign a p-high or wait for the crater run to finish and see what is says
(T-compiler is probably already aware of these issues)
